.TH CYGNUS-EDIT 1.2 "March 2026" "Version 1.2" "Cygnus Text Editor"
.SH NAME
cygnus-edit \- minimalist text editor for Cygnus WM

.SH SYNOPSIS
.B cygnus-edit
[\fIFILE\fR]

.SH DESCRIPTION
.B cygnus-edit
is a simple, fast text editor written for the Cygnus Window Manager. It provides basic text editing features with a minimalist interface.

.SH KEY BINDINGS
.TP
.B Ctrl+s
Save the current file.
.TP
.B Ctrl+q
Exit the editor.

